---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Section from "../components/ui/Section.astro";
---

<!-- Week 5 – SEO/OG meta: per-page title/description/ogType/ogImage -->
<!-- Edit these props if you want to change how the page appears in Google + social previews. -->

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Facial Volume Harmony"
  description="How Face Fitness handles email subscriptions, analytics consent, and third-party services. Learn what we collect and how you can manage consent."
  ogType="website"
  ogImage="https://cdn.facialvolumeharmony.com/og-images/og_hero-poster.png"
>
  <Section title="Privacy Policy">
    <div class="card">

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">1. Introduction</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
        This Privacy Policy explains how Facial Volume Harmony (“we”, “us”, or “our”) collects, uses, and protects your information when you visit our website.
        By using this website, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">2. Information We Collect</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
        We may collect the following types of information:
      </p>

      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
        <strong>a) Information you provide</strong><br />
        Email address (when you subscribe or contact us)
      </p>

      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
        <strong>b) Automatically collected information</strong><br />
        IP address<br />
        Device and browser type<br />
        Pages visited and interactions on the website
      </p>

      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
        This data is collected through analytics tools to help us understand and improve the user experience.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">3. How We Use Your Information</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
        We use your information to:
      </p>
      <ul style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;padding-left:20px;margin-top:10px;">
        <li>Provide and improve our website and content</li>
        <li>Communicate with you (if you subscribe)</li>
        <li>Send emails with updates, tips, and relevant content</li>
        <li>Ensure the security and functionality of the website</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">4. Cookies</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
        We use cookies to improve your experience and understand how the website is used.
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
        Cookies may be used for:
      </p>
      <ul style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;padding-left:20px;margin-top:10px;">
        <li>Website functionality</li>
        <li>Analytics (e.g. Google Analytics)</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
        You can accept or decline cookies through our cookie banner and manage your preferences at any time.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">5. Analytics (Google Analytics)</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
        We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors interact with the website.
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
        Google Analytics collects information such as:
      </p>
      <ul style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;padding-left:20px;margin-top:10px;">
        <li>pages visited</li>
        <li>time spent on the site</li>
        <li>general location (country-level)</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
        This data is processed in an aggregated and anonymized form where possible.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">6. Email Marketing</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
        If you subscribe to our emails, your information will be processed through our email marketing provider (e.g. MailerLite).
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
        We use your email to:
      </p>
      <ul style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;padding-left:20px;margin-top:10px;">
        <li>send updates</li>
        <li>share tips and content</li>
        <li>communicate relevant information about the program</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
        You can unsubscribe at any time by clicking the link in any email.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">7. Payments</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
        All payments are securely processed by a third-party provider (e.g. Lemon Squeezy).
        We do not store or have access to your payment details.
        For more information, please refer to the privacy policy of the payment provider.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">8. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
        If you are located in the European Economic Area (EEA), we process your data based on:
      </p>
      <ul style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;padding-left:20px;margin-top:10px;">
        <li>Your consent (e.g. cookies, email subscription)</li>
        <li>Legitimate interest (e.g. website analytics and improvement)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">9. Your Rights</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
        You have the right to:
      </p>
      <ul style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;padding-left:20px;margin-top:10px;">
        <li>Access your personal data</li>
        <li>Request correction or deletion</li>
        <li>Withdraw your consent at any time</li>
        <li>Object to data processing</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
        To exercise these rights, please contact us.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">10. Data Security</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
        We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information and ensure it is handled securely.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">11. Third-Party Services</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
        We may use third-party services such as:
      </p>
      <ul style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;padding-left:20px;margin-top:10px;">
        <li>Google Analytics</li>
        <li>Email marketing platforms (e.g. MailerLite)</li>
        <li>Payment providers (e.g. Lemon Squeezy)</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:12px;">
        These providers may process data according to their own privacy policies.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">12. Changes to This Policy</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3" style="margin-top:28px;">13. Contact</h3>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;">
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you can contact us at:
      </p>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);max-width:75ch;line-height:1.7;margin-top:10px;">
        📧 <a href="mailto:hello@facialvolumeharmony.com">hello@facialvolumeharmony.com</a>
      </p>


    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>